{"tid":1427879,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"切勿透露自己及其他人的個人資料","createTime":"2019-08-07T08:11:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T08:31:56.000Z","uid":100581,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8681039925355d64ec17b73d7a604d14285b24d1","tid":1427879,"uid":100581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:11:14.000Z","msg":"有消息傳出，在不只一間學校，有自稱「信得過」的人士開設群組，收集曾經發夢的學生之個人資料，包括電話號碼及TG ID，而群組內包括有聲稱信得過的教職員。<br />\n<br />\n我們提醒同道，為保障自己及他人安全，無論該群組聲稱有任何用途，敬請各位同道切勿隨意收集或向他人包括狀似可信的人士，透露自己及其他人的個人資料，又或是傳送發夢時的圖片及短片，以免令人有機可乘，成為義士的入罪證據。"},{"pid":"cdef59a6de11e9fc66a96d4c0189622acd076864","tid":1427879,"uid":100581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:12:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a0d81d43137e8f4a1edb98152b90b9982347208","tid":1427879,"uid":100581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:14:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58f49352c3f24f46d12ba112ad1b0e35c8aa5d73","tid":1427879,"uid":100581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:31:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}